    "Results General performance of ChatGPT-4 versus Gemini in English and ArabicA higher percentage of correct responses for both generative AI models was observed in English compared to Arabic despite the lack of statistical signi cance.",
    "For Gemini in Arabic, the total number of correct responses was 22/40 (55.0%) while the correct responses for the same MCQs in English was 25/40 (62.5%, P =.650, FET).",
    "A similar trend was observed for ChatGPT-4 with correct responses in Arabic at 26/40 (65.0%) compared to 32/40 (80.0%) in English (P =.210, FET).In Arabic, higher number of correct responses was seen in ChatGPT-4 compared to Gemini (65.0% vs.55.0%, P =.494, FET) and similarly higher number of correct responses was observed in English for ChatGPT-4 compared to Gemini (80.0% vs. 62.5%, P =.137, FET).",
